Installing NightWatch:
==============
- Make sure you have node/npm installed
- Create your project
- cd into your project folder
- npm init
- npm install -g nightwatch --save-dev

Setting up your project:
==============
- Create your test folder and you are ready to write your first test
- Create your nightwatch.json with the Selenium setup as well as the path to your test folder

Running your tests:
==============
$nightwatch
